OL,3,C'I think they're dead': Inquiry hears
OL,4,C999 calls made after Nottingham attacks
OL,6,FThe inquiry into the Nottingham
OL,7,Fattacks heard two 999 calls which were
OL,8,Fmade by witnesses moments after Grace
OL,9,FO'Malley Kumar and Barnaby Webber were
OL,10,Fstabbed in June 2023.
OL,12,FA caller cried and told police "my God
OL,13,Fthat's awful" as he reported that
OL,14,Fstudents Barnaby and Grace had been
OL,15,Fstabbed on Ilkeston Road in Nottingham.
OL,17,FOne of the first calls received by
OL,18,FNottinghamshire Police began: "There's
OL,19,Fbeen a stabbing on Ilkeston Road.
OL,21,F"There's somebody lying in the street.
OL,26,@tD@`OUuD@MO]zD@_OU}D@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/13
