OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1773493903
OL,3,C'I think they're dead': Inquiry hears
OL,4,C999 calls made after Nottingham attacks
OL,6,F"I think they're dead."
OL,8,FThe male caller said: "Oh, that was
OL,9,Fawful", repeating this a number of
OL,10,Ftimes as he became more emotional as
OL,11,Fthe call went on.
OL,13,FHe told the operator he saw a black
OL,14,Fman with a black bag, all dressed in
OL,15,Fblack go up Ilkeston Road towards the
OL,16,Ftown centre.
OL,18,FThe calls were played as
OL,19,FSuperintendent Simon Allardice, from
OL,20,FNottinghamshire Police, gave evidence
OL,21,Fon Day 12 of the inquiry.
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@WO]pD@WOUqD@FO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
