OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1773493903
OL,3,C'I think they're dead': Inquiry hears
OL,4,C999 calls made after Nottingham attacks
OL,6,FThe inquiry also heard that due to
OL,7,F"technical issues", some of the
OL,8,Femergency calls from the incident have
OL,9,Fbeen lost and have not been able to be
OL,10,Frecovered.
OL,12,FJulian Blake KC who was questioning
OL,13,Fthe officer, explained that Mr
OL,14,FAllardice was being called today to
OL,15,Festablish a timeline of the "factual
OL,16,Fevents" on June 13, when Valdo
OL,17,FCalocane fatally stabbed University of
OL,18,FNottingham undergraduates Mr Webber
OL,19,Fand Miss O'Malley-Kumar and
OL,20,Fgrandfather Ian Coates, 65.
OL,26,@wD@]OUxD@GO]
