OL,3,C'I think they're dead': Inquiry hears
OL,4,C999 calls made after Nottingham attacks
OL,6,FThe caller told the police there was
OL,7,Fan injured man who seemed to be in his
OL,8,F20s lying in the middle in the road.
OL,10,FHe said: "Blood all over their chest",
OL,11,Fand said again: "My God, that's awful."
OL,13,FThe caller, who explained he was
OL,14,Flooking out of his bedroom window from
OL,15,F500m away, said: "I heard lots of
OL,16,Fscreaming and looked out of the
OL,17,Fwindow."
OL,19,FHe said: "I think he's dead, he's not
OL,20,Fmoved a muscle."
