OL,3,C'I think they're dead': Inquiry hears
OL,4,C999 calls made after Nottingham attacks
OL,6,FWhen the operator asked if there was
OL,7,Fonly one victim, the caller said a
OL,8,Fgirl had also been stabbed.
OL,10,FHe said: "She was sat in a driveway of
OL,11,Fone of the eco-houses over the road
OL,12,Fbut I think she's wandered off down
OL,13,Fthe road.
OL,15,F"She was bleeding from the stomach.
OL,17,F"He stabbed both of them."
OL,19,FThe caller began crying as the
OL,20,Foperator asked him what the girl was
OL,21,Fwearing.
OL,26,@rD@JOUwD@AOUyD@AOUyD@ZO]
