OL,3,C'I think they're dead': Inquiry hears
OL,4,C999 calls made after Nottingham attacks
OL,6,FHe then told the operator police had
OL,7,Farrived and then said: "He's alive."
OL,9,FIn another 999 call made at about the
OL,10,Fsame time ` just after 4am ` a woman
OL,11,Ftold an operator there were two people
OL,12,F"in the road".
OL,14,FShe said: "I don't know if they've
OL,15,Fbeen stabbed. A girl and a guy. I
OL,16,Fthink they've been robbed or something.
OL,18,F"I heard them scream and I went there
OL,19,Fand I looked out the window and I saw
OL,20,Fsomeone. There's two people lying down
OL,21,Fthere."
