OL,3,C'I think they're dead': Inquiry hears
OL,4,C999 calls made after Nottingham attacks
OL,6,FShe said: "There's a guy and a girl.
OL,7,FThey're not too old. I don't know if
OL,8,Fthey're OK. Could you please come?
OL,9,FThey're lying down on the road right
OL,10,Fnow."
OL,12,FThe caller said the offender had
OL,13,F"walked off" and told police he was
OL,14,Fwearing a hoodie.
OL,16,FShe said: "He's gone. I can't see him
OL,17,Fanywhere in the road. But there's a
OL,18,Fperson lying down right there. He's
OL,19,Fstill there."
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@EO]uD@AOUuD@LO]xD@KOU{D@MO]
