OL,3,C'I think they're dead': Inquiry hears
OL,4,C999 calls made after Nottingham attacks
OL,6,FAnd she added: "I'm afraid to go out
OL,7,Fthere alone right now."
OL,9,FThe woman told the operator that she
OL,10,Fhad filmed what she saw.
OL,12,FEarlier, the chairwoman told the
OL,13,Finquiry that she had viewed the
OL,14,Ffootage of the "brutal attack" on the
OL,15,Fstudents but this will not be played
OL,16,Fin the inquiry.
OL,18,Fe inquiry was played a range of audio
OL,19,Fand video recordings which outlined
OL,20,Fhow the police responded to the
OL,21,Funfolding situation on June 13.
OL,26,@nD@POUoD@WO]vD@POUvD@^O]
