OL,3,C'I think they're dead': Inquiry hears
OL,4,C999 calls made after Nottingham attacks
OL,6,FThis included video of Calocane
OL,7,Fdriving Mr Coates's van around
OL,8,FNottingham city centre, with police
OL,9,Fdashcam footage capturing one of the
OL,10,Flater non-fatal collisions.
OL,12,FBorn-worn cameras also captured
OL,13,FCalocane being arrested in Bentinck
OL,14,FRoad.
OL,16,FThe footage showed an officer shouting
OL,17,F"stay where you are" before Tasering
OL,18,Fhim in the driver's seat of the van.
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@TO]
