OL,6,FAfter he is removed from the vehicle
OL,7,Fthe footage shows him being read his
OL,8,Frights as he lies face-up with his
OL,9,Fhands handcuffed in front of him.
OL,11,FHe replied "f*** you" when asked his
OL,12,Fname and what is in his bag by one of
OL,13,Fthe officers.
