OL,3,C'I think they're dead': Inquiry hears
OL,4,C999 calls made after Nottingham attacks
OL,6,FAfter Thursday's evidence, Mr Webber's
OL,7,Fmother, Emma Webber, said: "The
OL,8,Ftimeline set out today, accompanied by
OL,9,F999 calls, CCTV, police response,
OL,10,Faudio and video footage of Calocane's
OL,11,Frampage and arrest on the streets of
OL,12,FNottingham show the true nature and
OL,13,Fterror of this crime.
OL,26,@oD@\OU
