OL,3,C'I think they're dead': Inquiry hears
OL,4,C999 calls made after Nottingham attacks
OL,6,F"We were unable to sit throughout much
OL,7,Fof it as it is the stuff of the living
OL,8,Fhell we are forever in. As awful as
OL,9,Fthis is for anyone to bear it is
OL,10,Fbecause of the public inquiry that the
OL,11,Ftruth and painful detail of all of
OL,12,Fthis horror are rightly being exposed.
OL,13,FWrongs must be righted."
OL,15,FCalocane, who admitted manslaughter
OL,16,Fand attempted murder, is detained
OL,17,Findefinitely in a high-security
OL,18,Fhospital after prosecutors accepted
OL,19,Fhis not guilty pleas to murder at his
OL,20,Fsentencing at Nottingham Crown Court
OL,21,Fin January 2024.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@XO]
